OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start, with patchy
OL,6,Fdrizzle towards the west. Skies will
OL,7,Fbrighten in the east, though many
OL,8,Fwestern areas holding onto lots of
OL,9,Fcloud. Feeling warm, especially in the
OL,10,Fsunshine in the east, and muggy once
OL,11,Fagain.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud remains in the west but
OL,14,Fclear in the east. Cloud will thicken
OL,15,Fand lower across the region which can
OL,16,Fbring some outbreaks of rain and
OL,17,Fdrizzle at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
