OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA cloudy and dull start, but
OL,6,Fcloud once again breaks up in the
OL,7,Feast, but lingers in the west. Feeling
OL,8,Fvery warm in the sunshine and away
OL,9,Ffrom coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FTurning
OL,12,Fmore settled into the weekend as high
OL,13,Fpressure starts to build from the
OL,14,Fsouth. Sunny spells and feeling very
OL,15,Fwarm with temperatures well above the
OL,16,FJune average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
